.. _about_selection:

=====================
The Selection project
=====================

.. include:: ./links_names.txt

This is a project that collects various tools for
post-selection inference.


Jonathan Taylor was funded by NSF in writing their portion of the
software. As such, this material is based upon work supported by the
National Science Foundation under Grant DMS 1208857, and by the AFOSR
grant 113039.

Any opinions, findings, and conclusions or recommendations expressed
in this material are those of the author(s) and do not necessarily
reflect the views of the National Science Foundation.

